Texts.Chs: 进来吧，他们不会咬人的！也许吧。
Texts.Eng: Drop on in, they won't bite! Probably.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人发展旅游业业业。有利于资助下层建建建筑。
Texts.Eng: Florans expanding tourism indussstry. Good for funding infrassstructure.

Texts.Chs: 我可以想到其他几个我更愿意投资像素的项目，谢谢。
Texts.Eng: I could think of several other endeavors I would rather invest my pixels in, thank you.

Texts.Chs: 这里出售的小玩意还真是狩猎战利品...
Texts.Eng: Knickknacks are being sold here alongside very real hunting trophies...

Texts.Chs: 那么，那些骨头是假的，对吗？...大概不是。
Texts.Eng: So, uh, those bones are fake right? ... Probably not.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人的旅游纪念品库存惊人的丰富。
Texts.Eng: The Floran are surprisingly well stocked in tourist souvenirs.

Texts.Chs: 这些产品的质量值得一瞥，因为它们都是由植物或骨骼组成的。
Texts.Eng: The quality of these products is remarkable considering the whole of them are made up of either plants or bone.

Texts.Chs: 看看这个———一只由真正的吐舌娃皮制成的烧瓶。
Texts.Eng: Well lookit that - a flask made from genuine Poptop hide.
